@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = v1
    v2 = 0.97
    v2 = ((v0 / (v2 + 0.00 * tmp + 0.96)) + wp.abs((v0 + 0.87 / tmp + 0.29)))
    tmp = wp.cos(0.75)
    tmp = v1
    data[tid] = v0
